Property.Value: BEGIN SELECT SelectedCar.Id, SelectedCar.OwnerProfileId, CarBrand.Name AS Brand, CarModel.Name AS Model, CarNumber.Number AS Number FROM (SELECT * FROM Car WHERE Id = @CarId) AS SelectedCar LEFT JOIN CarBrand ON SelectedCar.BrandId = CarBrand.Id LEFT JOIN CarModel ON SelectedCar.ModelId = CarModel.Id LEFT JOIN CarNumber ON SelectedCar.NumberId = CarNumber.Id; END;
